700/MjE2MTk0NjIyMjkwOTI5MDA3/gemz-procter-and-gamble-launch-3.jpg\" srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" width=\"5350\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/phoenix-picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cp itemprop=\"author\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto: Courtesy of Gemz\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAlongside its portfolio of traditional shampoo brands (Pantene, Herbal Essences, Head \u0026amp; Shoulders, Aussie), P\u0026amp;G\u0026#39;s expansion into innovative and sustainably-minded \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/hair-care\"\u003ehair care\u003c/a\u003e is a response to shifting consumer attitudes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe conglomerate observed growing demand for solid shampoos and conditioners, but felt that the market\u0026#39;s current options fell short when it came to performance. \u0026#34;Consumers are responding to the concept because it offers high-performance beauty results without the fillers, buildup or waste of traditional liquid formats — plus the customizable, travel-friendly design fits seamlessly into their fast-moving, ever-changing routines,\u0026#34; shared Robert Reiss, brand vice president of North America Hair \u0026amp; Disruptive Innovation at P\u0026amp;G.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo introduce a new delivery system for shampoo and conditioner to consumers, P\u0026amp;G is employing digital-first storytelling and influencer campaigns to snag \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/gen-z\"\u003eGen Z\u003c/a\u003e (its target audience)\u0026#39;s attention. It selected Target as its first \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/retail\"\u003eretail\u003c/a\u003e partner due to its \u0026#34;strong Gen-Z customer base\u0026#34; that will help introduce the younger generation to water-activated hair care.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;Gemz was created for people who want hair care that adapts to them, even if their hair needs change every wash day,\u0026#34; Reiss added. \u0026#34;With Gemz, it\u0026#39;s easy to mix and match formulas to create the perfect routine.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAhead, see all of Gemz\u0026#39;s water-activated shampoo and conditioner offerings launching at Target.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-flat-gallery id=\"ci030013e53000256f\" config=\"{\u0026#34;items\u0026#34;:[{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e750002613\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;gemz_multipackpng\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e700002613\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;cn_lightasairpng\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e65001256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;cn_profoundmoisture\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e7a0002613\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;cn_quickblowdry\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e63000256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;cn_rainydayanti\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e6e0002613\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;cn_stressless\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e77000256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;sh_curlydays\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e83000256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;sh_hydrationlock\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e81000256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;sh_perfairdry\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci030013e80000256f\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;sh_upallday\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#